---
import { ArrowRight, ExternalLink } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section
    class="py-24 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 transition-colors"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12"
    >
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 transition-colors"
            >
                We ship projects.
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed transition-colors"
            >
                Hack Club isn't a class. It's a club. We don't have tests or
                grades. We have projects. Whether it's a personal portfolio, a
                discord bot, or a video game, you'll build something you're
                proud of.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                {
                    [
                        "Build your own website",
                        "Create a game in JS",
                        "Design a PCB",
                        "Deploy a web app",
                    ].map((item) => (
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">
                            <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full text-green-600">
                                <ArrowRight size={16} />
                            </div>
                            {item}
                        </li>
                    ))
                }
            </ul>
            <a
                href="https://hackclub.com/ship/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="text-[#ec3750] font-bold text-lg underline hover:decoration-wavy inline-flex items-center gap-2"
            >
                See what Hack Clubbers build <ExternalLink size={18} />
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 relative">
            <div
                class="bg-[#121217] rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-[#8492a6] dark:border-slate-600 transform md:rotate-3 transition-transform hover:rotate-0 duration-500"
            >
                <div
                    class="bg-[#17171D] p-3 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-[#8492a6] dark:border-slate-600"
                >
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                    <div
                        class="ml-4 bg-[#252429] rounded-md px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono w-full"
                    >
                        hackclub-project.js
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="p-6 font-mono text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"
                >
                    <p>
                        <span class="text-purple-400">const</span>
                        <span class="text-yellow-400">club</span> = <span
                            class="text-blue-400">new</span
                        >
                        <span class="text-green-400">HackClub</span>();
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-2">
                        <span class="text-purple-400">while</span> (club.members.length
                        &gt; 0)
                        {"{"}
                    </p>
                    <p class="ml-4 text-slate-400">// We build together</p>
                    <p class="ml-4">
                        <span class="text-yellow-400">club</span>.build(<span
                            class="text-orange-400">'Awesome Projects'</span
                        >);
                    </p>
                    <p class="ml-4">
                        <span class="text-yellow-400">club</span>.share(<span
                            class="text-orange-400">'Global Community'</span
                        >);
                    </p>
                    <p class="ml-4">
                        <span class="text-yellow-400">club</span>.haveFun(<span
                            class="text-blue-400">true</span
                        >);
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-2">{"}"}</p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 animate-pulse">_</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
